{
  "stem": "22447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- So you were just saying about you were watching Hamburg-- Yeah, we was in the field watching Hamburg burning at the time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was on a Friday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then a message comes through-- the British Second Army's come across a concentration camp in a place called Belsen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No one ever heard of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, well, what's going on there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said they want 17 volunteers to go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, the only thing you volunteer for is to go home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because if volunteers are wanted, there's an element of danger somewhere.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a sicky job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what, what, what is it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there's a lot of dead people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's thousands of dead people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like the leaves of autumn fall to the ground, so people are falling down on the ground, dead.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're just dying off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just lay in the road.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they, they die.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's-- typhus is running right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Dysentery is running right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "TB is running right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we've got to get some law and order, try and get something put together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was on a Friday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they want 17 volunteers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I thought to myself, well, if I don't go, who else should go?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did they identify clearly that any of them were Jewish?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or was there any mention of that at all?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they said-- I said, well, who are these people?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, well, the bulk of them are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was a, a sprinkling of gypsies-- they come from Hungary-- and some Russian prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the bulk of it was Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What we're going to find there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not to that extent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I had a cousin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- I'd never seen him, but he lives in Paris.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
